      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on an internal training module for our staff. we want to move beyond just teaching them not to click bad links. can you give me some specific red flags they should look for in spear-phishing emails that use social engineering? like, what are the subtle signs of someone trying to manipulate them?",
